To run in an environment:
- Within the main directory of the project type the following
    -> source setup.sh
    - This is an automated script to handle .venv and
      other dependancies
    - For the moment it is only automated for the macbook

- When testing the site...
    - Direct to the face_recognition_admin folder and user...
        -> python manage.py runserver command in the terminal

- When testing the face_recognition camera...
    - python src/face_recogntionn/face_recogntion.py
    - Should take a while to load up but should open 